Title: Helper Functions to Interact with the ICES SharePoint Using JWT Authentication
Authors@R: c(person("Colin", "Millar", role=c("aut","cre"), email="colin.millar@ices.dk"),
             person("Arni", "Magnusson", role=c("aut")),
